# Project Structure Guide

This is a Next.js 15 application using the App Router with TypeScript and Tailwind CSS.

## Key Files and Directories

- [app/layout.tsx](mdc:app/layout.tsx) - Root layout with metadata and global styles
- [app/page.tsx](mdc:app/page.tsx) - Main home page component
- [app/globals.css](mdc:app/globals.css) - Global CSS with Tailwind imports
- [app/components/](mdc:app/components/) - All React components

## Component Architecture

The main application logic is in [app/components/CountdownApp.tsx](mdc:app/components/CountdownApp.tsx), which:
- Manages URL state for countdown parameters
- Conditionally renders either the form or display based on URL state
- Handles client-side hydration

Key components:
- [CountdownForm.tsx](mdc:app/components/CountdownForm.tsx) - Form for creating countdowns
- [CountdownDisplay.tsx](mdc:app/components/CountdownDisplay.tsx) - Displays the countdown timer
- [DynamicHead.tsx](mdc:app/components/DynamicHead.tsx) - Dynamic meta tags
- [Header.tsx](mdc:app/components/Header.tsx) and [Footer.tsx](mdc:app/components/Footer.tsx) - Layout components

## Configuration Files

- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Dependencies and scripts
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration with path aliases
- [next.config.ts](mdc:next.config.ts) - Next.js configuration
- [eslint.config.mjs](mdc:eslint.config.mjs) - ESLint configuration
